"多头", "macd_signal": "✓ 多头排列，持续上涨", "rsi_6": 71.04220793049106, "rsi_12": 67.52432218875008, "rsi_24": 70.29157236053787, "rsi_status": "强势买入", "rsi_signal": "✅ RSI强势(67.5)，多头力量充足"}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': 'Understood, I have the pre-fetched data. Proceeding with analysis.'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '# Synthesis Request for 300308.SZ\nStock: 300308.SZ (中际旭创)\n\n## Agent Opinions\n\n### technical\nSignal: buy | Confidence: 0.70\nReasoning: 300308.SZ处于强势多头结构，MA5>MA10>MA20且均线发散上行，当前价1191.81仅小幅高于MA5（约+2.9%），符合不追高、回踩介入的节奏。MACD为多头且RSI维持强势区间（6/12/24日均在67-71附近），量能保持正常，短线延续概率较高。\nKey levels: {"support": 1158.47, "resistance": 1209.99, "stop_loss": 1044.32}\nExtra data: {"trend_score": 86, "ma_alignment": "bullish", "volume_status": "normal", "pattern": "none"}\n\nSynthesise the above into the Decision Dashboard JSON.'}], 'model': 'gpt-5.4-nano', 'temperature': 0.7}, 'extra_json': {}}
