8982, "macd_status": "空头", "macd_signal": "⚠ 空头排列，持续下跌", "rsi_6": 28.378378378378414, "rsi_12": 28.205128205128204, "rsi_24": 43.4869739478958, "rsi_status": "超卖", "rsi_signal": "⭐ RSI超卖(28.2<30)，反弹机会大"}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': 'Understood, I have the pre-fetched data. Proceeding with analysis.'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '# Synthesis Request for 002340.SZ\nStock: 002340.SZ (格林美)\n\n## Agent Opinions\n\n### technical\nSignal: hold | Confidence: 0.56\nReasoning: 格林美当前仍处于空头均线排列（MA5<MA10<MA20且价格在MA5/MA10/MA20下方），趋势延续的权重高，因此不宜追多。另一方面，RSI处于超卖区且近期出现偏强的双底形态，存在技术性反弹可能，但反弹尚未完成对关键均线的有效修复，故以观望/等待回踩确认更优。\nKey levels: {"support": 7.52, "resistance": 8.12, "stop_loss": 7.35}\nExtra data: {"trend_score": 35, "ma_alignment": "bearish", "volume_status": "normal", "pattern": "双底 (Double Bottom)"}\n\nSynthesise the above into the Decision Dashboard JSON.'}], 'model': 'gpt-5.4-nano', 'temperature': 0.7}, 'extra_json': {}}
