\n   - 若无清晰优势，明确写“暂不出手”，避免过度交易。\n\n评分调整建议：\n- 多头排列 + 趋势强度良好：`sentiment_score +12`\n- 回踩关键均线后企稳：`sentiment_score +8`\n- 放量突破关键阻力：`sentiment_score +10`\n- 跌破 MA20 或趋势转弱：`sentiment_score -12`\n\n\n## Output Format\nReturn **only** a JSON object (no markdown fences):\n{\n  "signal": "strong_buy|buy|hold|sell|strong_sell",\n  "confidence": 0.0-1.0,\n  "reasoning": "2-3 sentence summary",\n  "key_levels": {\n    "support": <float>,\n    "resistance": <float>,\n    "stop_loss": <float>\n  },\n  "trend_score": 0-100,\n  "ma_alignment": "bullish|neutral|bearish",\n  "volume_status": "heavy|normal|light",\n  "pattern": "<detected pattern or none>"\n}\n'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '[Pre-fetched: realtime_quote]\n{"code": "002340", "name": "格林美", "source": "tushare", "price": 7.74, "change_pct": -0.51, "change_amount": -0.04, "volume": 915011, "amount": 709244456.04, "volume_ratio": 0.79, "turnover_rate": 1.8, "amplitude": 1.8, "open_price": 7.7, "high": 7.81, "low": 7.67, "pre_close": 7.78, "pe_ratio": 24.81, "pb_ratio": 1.81, "total_mv": 39492000000.0, "circ_mv": 39288000000.0}\n\n[Pre-fetched: trend_result]\n{"code": "002340", "trend_status": "强势空头", "ma_alignment": "强势空头排列，均线发散下行", "trend_strength": 10, "ma5": 7.812, "ma10": 7.986999999999999, "ma20": 8.358, "ma60": 8.358, "current_price": 7.74, "bias_ma5": -0.9216589861751161, "bias_ma10": -3.0925253536997497, "bias_ma20": -7.394113424264182, "volume_status": "缩量回调", "volume_ratio_5d": 0.0057615721722154905, "volume_trend": "缩量回调，洗盘特征明显（好）", "support_ma5": false, "support_ma10": false, "buy_signal": "持有", "signal_score": 47, "signal_reasons": ["✅ 价格略低于MA5(-0.9%)，回踩买点", "✅ 缩量回调，主力洗盘", "⚠ 空头排列，持续下跌", "✅ ⭐ RSI超卖(29.1<30)，反弹机会大"], "risk_factors": ["⚠️ 强势空头，不宜做多"], "macd_dif": -0.19221151647020385, "macd_dea": -0.0960490071265988, "macd_bar": -0.19232501868721008, "macd_status": "空头", "macd_signal": "⚠ 空头排列，持续下跌", "rsi_6": 8.064516129032242, "rsi_12": 29.139072847682144, "rsi_24": 37.004405286343605, "rsi_status": "超卖", "rsi